    <item>
      <title>立法者表示，美国基地应禁止中国汽车技术</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/chinese-auto-tech-should-be-banned-at-us-bases-lawmakers-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国议员敦促五角大楼禁止采用中国技术的联网汽车进入美国军事基地，拜登政府对这些汽车构成的安全风险进行了调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/chinese-auto-tech-should-be-banned-at-us-bases-lawmakers-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 16:31:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国警方因苏格兰民族党财务问题再次逮捕男子</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/uk-police-re-arrest-man-over-scottish-national-party-finances</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国警方再次逮捕了一名 59 岁男子，该男子涉嫌对苏格兰民族党的资金和财务进行调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/uk-police-re-arrest-man-over-scottish-national-party-finances</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 16:04:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国政府即将任命新的邮局主席</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/uk-government-is-close-to-appointing-new-post-office-chair</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情人士透露，里希·苏纳克(Rishi Sunak)政府即将任命一位新的邮局主席，此前现任邮局主席在一月份因与部长们的争执而被罢免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/uk-government-is-close-to-appointing-new-post-office-chair</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 15:35:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非将对从美国进口的鸡肉征收反倾销税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/south-africa-to-keep-anti-dumping-duties-on-chicken-imports-from-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非贸易部长批准了一项建议，维持对原产于或从美国进口的冷冻带骨鸡肉部分征收反倾销税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/south-africa-to-keep-anti-dumping-duties-on-chicken-imports-from-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 15:19:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉反对派陷入混乱，马杜罗选择七月投票对手</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/venezuela-opposition-spirals-as-maduro-picks-rival-for-july-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名被禁止的候选人仍在竞选。她的替代者也被禁止参加比赛。分裂的反对派中的许多人认为，被允许参选的竞争者是他们想要击败的总统亲自挑选的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/venezuela-opposition-spirals-as-maduro-picks-rival-for-july-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 15:13:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民主党支持计划，乌克兰和以色列援助有望获得通过</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/ukraine-israel-aid-on-track-to-pass-as-democrats-back-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[长期停滞的对乌克兰、以色列和台湾的援助有望在国会获得通过，众议院民主党人纷纷支持议长迈克·约翰逊的计划，并提供选票来克服共和党保守派计划中的封锁企图。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/ukraine-israel-aid-on-track-to-pass-as-democrats-back-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 14:50:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>公民称肯尼亚国防军司令在直升机坠毁事件中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/kenya-defence-forces-chief-in-helicopter-crash-citizen-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《公民数字》报道，一架载有肯尼亚国防军司令弗朗西斯·奥戈拉将军的军用直升机在乌干达边境附近的偏远地区坠毁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/kenya-defence-forces-chief-in-helicopter-crash-citizen-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 14:07:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗称以色列的威胁可能引发核政策转变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/iran-threatens-strike-on-israeli-nuclear-sites-if-it-s-attacked</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗一名高级将领表示，如果以色列威胁攻击其核设施，伊朗可能会重新考虑其核政策，这是一个含蓄的警告，称德黑兰可能会竞相开发核武器，因为 4 月 13 日无人机和导弹袭击后，言论持续升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/iran-threatens-strike-on-israeli-nuclear-sites-if-it-s-attacked</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 13:08:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
